parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Airbag Module Failure and Recall Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag module can cause the airbags to deploy incorrectly or not deploy at all, leading to serious injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: Airbag warning light illumination
failure of airbags to deploy in an accident
inability to repair or replace airbags due to parts unavailability.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Inability to Obtain Recall Repairs Due to Parts Unavailability
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The inability to obtain recall repairs due to parts unavailability can leave drivers with defective airbags, putting them at risk of serious injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: Inability to schedule recall repairs
parts unavailability
long wait times for repairs
lack of communication from dealerships and manufacturers.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Failure of Dealerships to Perform Recall Repairs
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of dealerships to perform recall repairs can leave drivers with defective airbags, putting them at risk of serious injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: Dealerships unable or unwilling to perform recall repairs
lack of communication from dealerships
failure to provide loaner vehicles.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The detachment of the front bumper can cause a loss of control, accidents, or damage to the vehicle and surrounding property.
symptoms: The front bumper detaches from the vehicle without incident
requiring repair or reattachment.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Severe frame rust can compromise the structural integrity of the vehicle, leading to safety issues and potential accidents.
symptoms: Excessive rust on the vehicle's frame
potentially causing damage to other components.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Door latch failure can cause doors to open while driving, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Doors open unexpectedly while driving
often due to faulty latch assemblies made of plastic.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The detachment of the bed liner can cause a loss of control, accidents, or damage to the vehicle and surrounding property.
symptoms: The bed liner detaches from the bed of the vehicle while driving
potentially causing damage or obstruction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of exterior lighting, including headlights, taillights, and brake lights, can increase the risk of accidents, especially at night or in low-visibility conditions.
symptoms: Headlights
taillights
and brake lights fail to illuminate or work intermittently
making it difficult for other drivers to see the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake light switch can cause the brake lights to fail to illuminate, increasing the risk of rear-end collisions.
symptoms: Brake lights fail to illuminate when the brake pedal is depressed
and the vehicle may be involved in a rear-end collision.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the multifunction switch can cause various exterior lights to fail, including brake lights, taillights, and headlights, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Various exterior lights fail to illuminate or work intermittently
making it difficult for other drivers to see the vehicle.
